1907
01:51:21,808 --> 01:51:23,888
- You are hypnotist?
- No, of course not.

1908
01:51:23,928 --> 01:51:26,808
Well, then why am I seeing
all these strange things?

1909
01:51:26,848 --> 01:51:29,048
Don't you understand, George?

1910
01:51:29,088 --> 01:51:31,048
